snippet.description:
Longplay /complete playthrough of the 1984 C64 tennis classic Match Point aka Tournament Tennis. Published 1 March 2018.

Match Point is longplay No. 182 of the Ludophiles longplays project:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5rpA9sB1_-K_x5s207hoahb
